name: Little Witch Cafe
description:
This Little Witch Cafe is a space to look around and relax. Feel free to look around and enjoy the space.

Controls

W,A,S,D - Movement

Space - Jump

Description

Little Witch Cafe was a group studnet project to challage us with 3D modeling and level staging and deisgn. All models (except the cat) are made by studnets. There are no tasks within the room it is just a fun little space to explore
